This made me smile. However:



Following transfiguration, surviving subjects report being transported to an unknown location, SCP-5581-1.
附加记录：    

This makes it sound like they only report being transported, and actually remain in place. You should make it explicit that they suddenly disappear after the transformation, and reappear in the same place approximately [x] minutes/hours/days/whatever later. I was confused there for a second.

Anyways, +1. I first thought of pool when you said , and then I thought of ping pong when I considered the divisor, and then it turned out to be tennis! And now the pun makes sense.

Also, fantastic imagery for the transformation. I was actually able to follow it and visualize it.







